name: LORE_CONTEST_01 // AVATAR435 in the cyber disco
description:
Outside it’s dark, AI’s drones have swept the streets, hunting down AVATARS!
#435 found it’s way inside an underground place where people are partying like there is no tomorrow.
The NEON disco light helps #435 to become invisible until the drones are gone and the mission can proceed // Fanart by @cryptemes for lore_contest_01
